  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK795">
<l>aḻaccolli yalla tiṭittu vaḻakkaṟiya</l>
<l>vallārnaṭ pāyntu koḷal</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You should examine and secure the friendship of those who can speak so as to make you weep over a crime (before its commission) or rebuke you severely (after you have done it) and are able to teach you (the ways of) the world.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
